{"results":[{"aya":"008","id":5427,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"然后我大声召唤他们，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"009","id":5428,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"然后我公开地训导他们，秘密地劝谏他们，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"010","id":5429,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"我说，你们应当向你们的主求饶--他确是至赦的--","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"011","id":5430,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"他就使丰足的雨水降临你们，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"012","id":5431,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"并且以财产和子嗣援助你们，为你们创造园圃和河流。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"013","id":5432,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"你们怎么不希望真主的尊重呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"014","id":5433,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"他确已经过几个阶段创造了你们。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":4,"previousPage":"/zh/s071.json","nextPage":"/zh/s071-3.json"}}